{"tid":208782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［繼兒動母😛]15歲仔狂性大發 刀嚇繼母胸襲摸下體","createTime":"2017-04-19T18:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T18:26:11.000Z","uid":83052,"like":187,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b068bb538ceff5d2c539b4497bf4773c82990fb","tid":208782,"uid":83052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:00:10.000Z","msg":"柴灣翠灣邨發生風化案。今早8時許，一名15歲姓黃中三男生突然手持一把生果刀，將刀架於正準備出門返工的43歲繼母頸上，並向她胸襲摸下體大肆非禮。黃男其後拿出膠紙有所企圖，繼母奮力掙扎狂叫救命，鄰居聞言趕至喝止。警員接報到場，將黃男拘捕，他報稱糾纏間手部受傷，繼母亦感不適，兩人一併送東區醫院治理。東區警區重案組第二隊接手跟進，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器及非禮拘捕黃男。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170419/56585082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170419%2F56585082&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5e3d6444\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170419%2F56585082&h=fdbb3b59\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170419/56585082</a><br />\n<br />\nMilf <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb9b8d33657a1c72656ea753f8db663e9b0a6dc","tid":208782,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553de9f4da5b1e72f057bc7c6ce8460ba24569d0","tid":208782,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"AV情節<img src=\"/